1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to revenue and taxation; to amend section
2 77-2704.13, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska; to provide a sales
3 and use tax exemption for electricity, natural gas, propane, and
4 sewer utilities as prescribed; to provide an operative date; and to
5 repeal the original section.
